summary: Shot Through the Heart - gloomy - 방탄소년단 | Bangtan Boys | BTS [Archive of Our Own]
title: Shot Through the Heart - gloomy - 방탄소년단 | Bangtan Boys | BTS [Archive of Our Own]
excerpt: An Archive of Our Own, a project of the Organization for Transformative Works
description:
Chapters: 1/1
Fandom: 방탄소년단 | Bangtan Boys | BTS
Rating: Teen And Up Audiences
Warnings: No Archive Warnings Apply
Relationships: Jeon Jungkook/Park Jimin
Characters: Jeon Jungkook, Park Jimin (BTS), Jung Hoseok | J-Hope, Kim Namjoon | Rap Monster, Kim Taehyung | V, Kim Seokjin | Jin, Min Yoongi | Suga
Additional Tags: Canon Compliant, Drinking to Cope, although i suppose that is subtle, alternatively titled: 4 times jungkook confessed and the 1 time jimin accepts, Fluff, slight angst, [strums guitar] here have 2 boys in love
Summary:

“Jiminie-hyung, why don’t you like me?”

“What?” Jimin nervously chuckles, stopping his soothing motions on the younger’s scalp. “Of course I like you.”

"No, hyung,” Jungkook finally looks up from his spot in Jimin’s lap, eyes shining with unshed tears. “Why don’t you like like me?”

 -

Or: Jungkook has a habit of confessing his affections while drunk, and Jimin never thought to take him seriously.
